x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">On the one hand, th=
is is the kind of comment you would expect the C.E.O. of a $60 billion ente=
rprise-value company to make. C.E.O.s of big companies like to be able to m=
ake strategic moves in order to stay competitive, especially when their ind=
ustry is being bombarded by new competition and macroeconomic factors that =
are crushing profits and restricting their maneuverability. The last thing =
they want, in those circumstances, is a regulatory environment that makes i=
t difficult for them to flex. And as everyone who attends the Sun Valley co=
nference knows only too well, that=E2=80=99s what the <b>Biden</b> administ=
ration has confronted them with by putting <b>Lina Khan</b> in charge of th=
e Federal Trade Commission. <br/><br/>But what made Zaz=E2=80=99s comments =
so poignant, I think, is that he=E2=80=99s a lifelong Democrat who grew up =
in a two-bedroom apartment in
Brooklyn. Yes, he=E2=80=99s come a long way since then=E2=80=94he owns the =
requisite homes in East Hampton and Beverly Hills and his various boards of=
 directors have paid him a monumental fortune over the years=E2=80=94but he=
=E2=80=99s still a Democrat who supports the Biden administration and speak=
s regularly to <b>Gina</b> <b>Raimondo</b>, the Commerce Secretary. (Earlie=
r today, obviously, Biden announced he wasn=E2=80=99t running for reelectio=
n. I=E2=80=99d still expect Zaz to support whoever replaces Biden at the to=
p of the ticket.)<br/><br/>Moreover, two months after the expiry of the Rev=
erse Morris restrictions on Zaz=E2=80=99s merger of Discovery Communication=
s and the WarnerMedia assets, it suggests that Zaz is looking to deal, coll=
aborate, explore=E2=80=94anything, in fact, to boost his stock price. And t=
he comments were magnified and crystallized by two other events last week, =
as my partner <b>Matt Belloni</b> has brilliantly <u><a href=3D"https://ema=
il.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dRMTRZZWQ0Vk9fQU=
tmMGoyd0lRVT0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wdWNrLm5ld3MvYW5hbHlzdHMtZnVydGhlci1zb=
3VyLW9uLWRhdmlkLXphc2xhdnMtd2FybmVyLWJyb3MtZGlzY292ZXJ5Lz91dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249=
RHJ5K1Bvd2RlcistK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODclMkYyMSUyRjI0JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX2NvbnR=
